{"tid":1598861,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"全撚部入黎，係時候搵番你既初衷","createTime":"2019-09-27T16:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:59:14.000Z","uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7c669e3d57160d477e3fa3fc1ff790875ad6b4","tid":1598861,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"我相信大家聽完今晚新屋嶺集會事件之後<br />\n大家都會嬲撚到震<br />\n但我想起01/10依個非常重要既日子上面<br />\n提提大家聽番天琦係民族黨上面所講既每一句說話<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=8cb16b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但如果我地依班人，以及社會上好多未嚟嘅人，繼續保持依個夢想嘅話，我地一定可以實現依個夢想，一定會成功。 <br />\n<br />\n係呢一刻，非常之黑暗，但我相信大家都睇過蝙蝠俠，咁蝙蝠俠裡面有一句對白，就係話黎明之前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗。真係好黑暗，但係黎明即將會來臨。多謝大家。 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8bb8a550acfae441afb271b79eecd7ad0c125f27","tid":1598861,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推 大家要keep住行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fa517b0bce15882befbdd9dbdfa22233fb04e0","tid":1598861,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！"}]}